---
// No props needed
---

<section class="resume-section scroll-reveal-animate">
  <h2>Projects</h2>
    <div class="project-entry">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="institution"
        ><strong>Weather Impact on Energy Consumption	</strong></span
      >
      <span class="date">Present</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="details">
      <li>
        Developed a predictive model to forecast daily electricity demand using data from the U.S. Energy Information Administration (EIA) and NOAA weather stations
      </li>
      <li>
        Collected and preprocessed datasets, including electricity demand and time-series weather variables 
      </li>
      <li>
        Performed data cleaning, handling missing values, and merging multiple datasets
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="project-entry">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="institution"
        ><strong>Water Potability</strong></span
      >
      <span class="date">4 months</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="details">
      <li>
        Developed a data analysis pipeline to evaluate water potability and identify models with low
        prediction error
      </li>
      <li>
        Performed data cleaning, feature analysis, and error evaluation to improve classification accuracy
      </li>
      <li>
        Created visual statistical summaries (distributions, correlations, and trends) to enhance
        interpretability and user understanding
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="project-entry">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="institution"><strong>Grocery Store Database</strong></span>
      <span class="date">4 Months</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="details">
      <li>
        Built a structured SQL database to model a grocery store’s products, employees, and operational
        data

      </li>
      <li>
        Implemented queries to track inventory levels and generate product and employee based reports
      </li>
      <li>
        Created visual reports and graphs to demonstrate the database functionality and support project
        goals
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="project-entry">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="institution"><strong>Cased-Based Simulation</strong></span>
      <span class="date">4 Months</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="details">
      <li>
        Created an application for developers/users to create and take
        decision based simulations
      </li>
      <li>
        Developed a noSQL database to store simulations and
        developer/user information
      </li>
      <li>
        Maintained AGILE and consistent communication with sponsor to ensure requirements were
        completed
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>


  <p class="more-projects-link">
    For more projects, check the <a href="/projects">Projects page</a>.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .resume-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 1.5rem + 1.5vw, 2.8rem);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--text-muted);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  ul {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }
  .project-entry {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem; /* Space between entries */
  }
  .project-entry:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .project-entry .header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .project-entry .date {
    font-family: var(--font-family-sans);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .project-entry .details {
    list-style: disc; /* Use bullet points */
    padding-left: 1.5rem; /* Standard padding for list */
    margin-left: 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .project-entry .details li {
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .project-entry .header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .project-entry .date {
      margin-top: 0.3rem;
    }
  }

  .more-projects-link {
    margin-top: 3rem; /* Add space above this line */
    font-size: 1.2 rem;
  }
</style>
